                    <span>I just recently upgraded my computer from xp pro service pack one to service pack 2, and i totally regret it. Service pack 2 hardly ever inializes the proper drivers for anything including games. It also keep asking me to activate my copy long after i installed it. I had to install a patch to get around that problem. I still have to do a system restore every month just so i can keep using my pc. I would not recommend service pack 2 to anyone.</span>
                  
              
